			</div>
			<ul class="features group">
				<li>
					<div class="sprite discover">Discover</div>
					<h4 class="din med">Discover</h4>
					<p class="description">The best new apps and tools for social change</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="sprite curate">Curate</div>
